    "description": "在这款2D横向卷轴策略游戏中释放你的策略天赋——你必须建立基地、管理资源、探索神秘森林并征服敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391650/extras/692d265dff06ec7a298a6388781538c4.poster.avif?t=1730909330\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391650/extras/692d265dff06ec7a298a6388781538c4.webm?t=1730909330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391650/extras/692d265dff06ec7a298a6388781538c4.mp4?t=1730909330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 打造一支将会一直追随你并听你号令的军队！<br></li><li> 在每个夜晚保卫你的基地。<br></li><li> 体验攻城机制，对抗攻城专用的冲撞车、攻城塔和投石车。<br></li><li> 探索神秘的森林并揭开其中的秘密。<br></li><li> 对你的王国进行微管理，例如取消特定工作和进行狩猎。<br></li><li> 通过本地分屏合作与亲朋好友一起游玩。<br></li><li> 经历春夏秋冬的季节更替。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2391650/extras/ec36565ab1feab2be431ec1497629832.avif?t=1730909330\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
